<div id="who" class="tab-content active">
  <h2>Who I Am</h2>
  <img src="https://i.imgur.com/DiZwHoh.png" alt="Milko's Profile" class="profile-image" />
  <p>Hello, I'm Milko. I haven’t been on the internet long — I’m an unknown developer. I was born on April 10 (10/04).</p>
  <p>I live and was born in Mexico, Baja California. I won’t say the city for obvious reasons. I like making friends and hate internet fights — they’re dumb and ridiculous. Everyone ends up looking like fools. Still, it’s funny to argue, so I join in. I'm a badly made clown, literally. And I like that.</p>
</div>

<div id="what" class="tab-content">
  <h2>What I Am</h2>
  <p>I’m a human. END.</p>
  <p>Well… not the end yet. I’m a developer. I like to help and make games for fun. I haven’t released one yet and usually change ideas midway.</p>
  <p>I’m also a composer… okay, not really. I’m learning. I like designing and thinking of epic things — though I never really succeed. o_0</p>
</div>

<div id="like" class="tab-content">
  <h2>What I Like</h2>
  <p>I enjoy creating games, drawing, designing, and making OCs when I can. I’ve made two simple 3D models of my OCs.</p>
  <p>I like composing music — not very good ones, though I can make good melodies (just one). I struggle with basslines or drums, and I can’t use instruments in FL Studio well.</p>
  <p>Like many from newer (and not-so-new) generations, I love playing with my virtual friends, talking about fandoms and my projects.</p>
  <p>I love retro stuff — like old Roblox (2006–2017), the old web, and vintage vibes, even though I wasn’t born in those years. The past attracts me more than the present.</p>
</div>

<div id="extra" class="tab-content">
  <h2>Extra</h2>
  <p>I like bread, chocomilk, ice cream, and chilaquiles. I hate sour cream (not whipped cream — the other horrible one).</p>
  <p>I don’t have many real-life friends. I’m not very pleasant, and I don’t speak much English. I tend to say random stuff, stutter a lot, and can’t explain things clearly. I’m confusing to listen to.</p>
</div>

<div id="social" class="tab-content">
